data.description: MOTIVATED SELLER!! Welcome to this stunning Move-in ready home located in the highly sought-after area of Unionville. Situated on over an acre of land, this property offers both space and tranquility. With 4 bedrooms, 2 1/2 bathrooms, and an additional bonus room, there is plenty of room for the whole family. The primary suite, located on the main floor, features a trey ceiling, adding an elegant touch to the room. The en-suite bathroom includes a separate stand-up shower and a luxurious garden tub, providing the perfect oasis for relaxation. As the summer approaches, you'll love spending time on the screened-in porch, enjoying the gentle breeze and taking a refreshing dip in the above-ground pool. The property also boasts a spacious 2-car garage and an additional 25x25 wired shop, offering endless possibilities for storage or hobbies. Don't miss out on the chance to make this beautiful home yours - schedule your showings today!
